AI Chat Application

This project is a full stack AI powered chat application that allows users to interact with an intelligent assistant in real time. It includes a modern React frontend and a FastAPI backend integrated with an AI model. The application supports multiple chat sessions, persistent history, and a clean user interface similar to modern conversational platforms.

Project Overview

The application enables users to start a chat session, send messages, and receive AI generated responses. Each conversation is stored locally, allowing users to manage multiple chats. The frontend communicates with a deployed backend API to process and return responses.

Features

User login with name based session
Multiple chat sessions
Persistent chat history using local storage
Real time message streaming effect
Copy assistant responses
Responsive and clean user interface
Frontend deployed on Vercel
Backend deployed on Render

