Installation and Setup

Clone the repository

git clone your repository link

Navigate to frontend

cd ai chat frontend

Install dependencies

npm install

Start development server

npm start

Navigate to backend

cd ai chat backend

Create virtual environment

python -m venv venv

Activate environment

venv scripts activate

Install dependencies

pip install -r requirements.txt

Run backend server

uvicorn main app reload

Environment Variables

Create a .env file in backend and add your API key

GROQ API KEY your key here

Deployment

Frontend is deployed using Vercel. Any changes pushed to the main branch trigger automatic deployment.

Backend is deployed using Render. Ensure the API endpoint URL is correctly configured in the frontend.

Usage

Open the deployed frontend link
Enter your name to start
Create or switch chats
Send messages and receive responses

